stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> IDLE

    IDLE --> HAS_MONEY : insertCoin / bank coin
    IDLE --> IDLE : selectProduct ✗ (NEED_MONEY)

    HAS_MONEY --> HAS_MONEY : insertCoin / add money
    HAS_MONEY --> IDLE : cancel / refund
    HAS_MONEY --> DISPENSING : selectProduct ✓ (guards pass)

    DISPENSING --> IDLE : drop product +<br/>pay change, reset balance
    DISPENSING --> DISPENSING : any action ✗ (MACHINE_BUSY)

    note left of HAS_MONEY
        selectProduct ✗ → stay in
        HAS_MONEY, keep money, if:
        invalid code / out-of-stock /
        insufficient funds / no change
    end note

    note right of DISPENSING
        Transient: entered and left
        inside one selectProduct call.
        The lock point if dispensing
        ever becomes async.
    end note
